19#include <sys/cdefs.h>
20#ifndef lint
21__RCSID("$NetBSD: print-msdp.c,v 1.6 2017/02/05 04:05:05 spz Exp $");
22#endif
23
24/* \summary: Multicast Source Discovery Protocol (MSDP) printer */
25
26#ifdef HAVE_CONFIG_H
27#include "config.h"
28#endif
29
30#include <netdissect-stdinc.h>
31
32#include "netdissect.h"
33#include "addrtoname.h"
34#include "extract.h"
35
36#define MSDP_TYPE_MAX 7
37
38void
39msdp_print(netdissect_options *ndo, const u_char *sp, u_int length)
40{
41 unsigned int type, len;
42
43 ND_TCHECK2(*sp, 3);
44 /* See if we think we're at the beginning of a compound packet */
45 type = *sp;
46 len = EXTRACT_16BITS(sp + 1);
47 if (len > 1500 || len < 3 || type == 0 || type > MSDP_TYPE_MAX)
48 goto trunc; /* not really truncated, but still not decodable */
49 ND_PRINT((ndo, " msdp:"));
50 while (length > 0) {
51 ND_TCHECK2(*sp, 3);
52 type = *sp;
53 len = EXTRACT_16BITS(sp + 1);
54 if (len > 1400 || ndo->ndo_vflag)
55 ND_PRINT((ndo, " [len %u]", len));
56 if (len < 3)
57 goto trunc;
58 sp += 3;
59 length -= 3;
60 switch (type) {
61 case 1: /* IPv4 Source-Active */
62 case 3: /* IPv4 Source-Active Response */
63 if (type == 1)
64 ND_PRINT((ndo, " SA"));
65 else
66 ND_PRINT((ndo, " SA-Response"));
67 ND_TCHECK(*sp);
68 ND_PRINT((ndo, " %u entries", *sp));
69 if ((u_int)((*sp * 12) + 8) < len) {
70 ND_PRINT((ndo, " [w/data]"));
71 if (ndo->ndo_vflag > 1) {
72 ND_PRINT((ndo, " "));
73 ip_print(ndo, sp + *sp * 12 + 8 - 3,
74 len - (*sp * 12 + 8));
75 }
76 }
77 break;
78 case 2:
79 ND_PRINT((ndo, " SA-Request"));
80 ND_TCHECK2(*sp, 5);
81 ND_PRINT((ndo, " for %s", ipaddr_string(ndo, sp + 1)));
82 break;
83 case 4:
84 ND_PRINT((ndo, " Keepalive"));
85 if (len != 3)
86 ND_PRINT((ndo, "[len=%d] ", len));
87 break;
88 case 5:
89 ND_PRINT((ndo, " Notification"));
90 break;
91 default:
92 ND_PRINT((ndo, " [type=%d len=%d]", type, len));
93 break;
94 }
95 sp += (len - 3);
96 length -= (len - 3);
97 }
98 return;
99trunc:
100 ND_PRINT((ndo, " [|msdp]"));
101}
